OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cooler and fresher start to
OL,6,FMonday morning for all of us. A dry
OL,7,Fday will follow with some fair weather
OL,8,Fcloud and sunny spells throughout.
OL,9,FMostly light winds and feeling
OL,10,Fpleasant in the sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLight winds and sunny spells
OL,13,Fto end the day. However, cloud will
OL,14,Fincrease from the west overnight, with
OL,15,Fa little light rain possible on
OL,16,Fwestern hills. A slightly milder night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
