OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FRather cloudy to start the
OL,6,Fday, the cloud then tending to break
OL,7,Fup a little allowing frequent showers
OL,8,Fto develop, some heavy with thunder
OL,9,Fpossible towards the north.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,12,Fmostly dry, settled spell of weather
OL,13,Fwith bright or sunny spells. A spell
OL,14,Fof rain likely into Thursday.
OL,15,FTemperatures near average, but slowly
OL,16,Fedging up.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
